            <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding:6px 14px; border-radius:20px; font-weight:600; font-size:0.85rem; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">🔴 Red Dot Product Design Award</div>
            <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding:6px 14px; border-radius:20px; font-weight:600; font-size:0.85rem; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">🏆 iF Design Award</div>
